
# 🎮 Game Recommender — Frontend

A production-grade React SPA for discovering PC games based on your hardware specs.

---

## Tech Stack

| Tech | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| React 18 | UI Framework |
| React Router v6 | Client-side routing |
| Axios | HTTP requests |
| Context API | Global state (Auth) |

---

## Project Structure

```
frontend/
├── public/
│   └── index.html
├── src/
│   ├── pages/
│   │   ├── Home.jsx         # Landing page
│   │   ├── Login.jsx        # Authentication
│   │   ├── Register.jsx     # Account creation
│   │   ├── Dashboard.jsx    # Browse all games
│   │   ├── Recommend.jsx    # Hardware input + results
│   │   └── AdminPanel.jsx   # Game CRUD (Admin)
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── Navbar.jsx          # Navigation bar
│   │   ├── GameCard.jsx        # Game display card
│   │   ├── HardwareForm.jsx    # Spec input form
│   │   └── ProtectedRoute.jsx  # Route guard
│   ├── services/
│   │   └── api.js              # All Axios API calls
│   ├── context/
│   │   └── AuthContext.jsx     # Auth global state
│   ├── App.jsx                 # Root + routes
│   └── index.js               # Entry point
└── package.json
```

---

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Install Dependencies

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
```

### 2. Configure Environment (optional)

```bash
# .env
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
```

### 3. Start Development Server

```bash
npm start
# Runs on http://localhost:3000
```

---

## Pages & Routes

| Route | Page | Access |
|-------|------|--------|
| `/` | Home | Public |
| `/login` | Login | Public |
| `/register` | Register | Public |
| `/dashboard` | Game Library | Public |
| `/recommend` | Get Recommendations | Authenticated |
| `/admin` | Admin Panel | Admin only |

---

## Frontend → Backend Mapping

| Page | Method | Endpoint |
|------|--------|----------|
| Register.jsx | POST | `/api/auth/register` |
| Login.jsx | POST | `/api/auth/login` |
| Dashboard.jsx | GET | `/api/games` |
| Recommend.jsx | POST | `/api/recommend` |
| AdminPanel.jsx | POST/PUT/DELETE | `/api/games` |

---

## Authentication

JWT token stored in `localStorage`. Automatically attached to every request via Axios interceptor. On 401 response, user is auto-logged-out and redirected to `/login`.

---

## Key Features

- **Recommendation Engine UI** — Enter CPU/RAM/GPU/Storage and get ranked game matches
- **Match Score** — Each result shows a 0–100% compatibility score
- **Hardware Presets** — Quick-fill "Low-end", "Mid-range", "High-end", "Gaming Beast"
- **Genre & Platform Filters** — Filter the game library by multiple categories
- **Admin Panel** — Full game CRUD with inline table editing
- **Role-based Routing** — `ProtectedRoute` guards user and admin pages
- **Global Auth State** — via React Context API

---

## Design System

- Color palette: Deep navy + purple accent (`#6c63ff`) on dark backgrounds
- Dark theme throughout (`#0a0a14` base)
- Glassmorphism-style cards with gradient borders
- Responsive grid layouts for game cards